5. Preserve Tree but modify only one node
/////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

Eg. Insert into BST, Delete from BST, Trim Tree, etc 
Keep entire tree same, but modify only one node 
Core idea: Attach something new to existing tree

TreeNode helper(TreeNode node, ...) {
    if (node == null) {
        // base: create/return something
        return NEW_NODE_OR_NULL;
    }

    if (goLeft) {
        node.left = helper(node.left, ...);
    } else {
        node.right = helper(node.right, ...);
    }

    // optionally update node (rare for BST insert)
    return node;  // return SAME node (structure preserved)
}